Startup-log excerpts for issue #580, captured per scenario into isolated profile roots
(CC_DIRECTOR_ROOT under %TEMP%) so each scenario starts clean and the real per-user credential is
never touched. Profile-root paths are redacted to %TEMP% (they were under the test user's temp dir).

